WEBVTT

00:00:43.090 --> 00:00:50.960
[Sharp Blade in the Snow]

00:00:51.030 --> 00:00:53.930
[Episode 19]

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:56.400
I thought

00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:57.480
Xiqi forced you

00:00:57.480 --> 00:00:58.960
into this political marriage.

00:00:58.960 --> 00:00:59.440
But now...

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:01.720
The Queen of Mocheng is quite beautiful.

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:03.680
But I'm also good-looking.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:06.200
She will marry into Xiqi.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:09.240
Why don't you consider me instead,
Stone King of Hell?

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:14.880
You got me out of jail

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:16.010
and gave me freedom,

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:18.280
I'll help you out of this situation

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:20.010
and give you freedom in return.

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:25.380
This marriage isn’t something
to play around with.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:27.880
The Young Master of Xiqi

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:29.880
has to return with me to Mocheng

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:31.240
as the Imperial Consort

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:33.440
to form an alliance through marriage.

00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:35.840
This is the only way to
protect both cities.

00:01:36.160 --> 00:01:38.160
Princess Xin Miao is brave.

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:40.520
Young Master Xin Yao is wise.

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:43.320
The Xin family is virtuous and kind.

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:45.490
Even if it costs my life,

00:01:46.120 --> 00:01:47.280
I will never let

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:49.400
Meng Wu take control of Mocheng.

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:56.000
For Xiqi

00:01:56.160 --> 00:01:57.080
and Mocheng,

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:58.880
we must do this.

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.320
Stone King of Hell, you are a righteous man.

00:02:02.800 --> 00:02:03.880
I hope you

00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:05.980
can prioritize the greater good.

00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:10.300
Dongli has fallen.

00:02:10.639 --> 00:02:12.400
I understand the pain of
losing one's homeland,

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:13.930
and the suffering of exile.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:17.800
Li.

00:02:18.320 --> 00:02:20.380
Since you carry such righteousness,

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:22.400
I won't stop you.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.760
I'll escort you back to Mocheng.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.480
He is truly remarkable

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:34.560
and broad-minded.

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.000
Since you two broke up anyway,

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:38.960
what about giving him to me?

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.880
Stone King of Hell is renowned

00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:42.840
in Xiqi.

00:02:48.200 --> 00:02:49.480
We can negotiate.

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:52.140
If he can't marry me,
recruitment works too.

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.760
I think you have no chance.

00:02:57.880 --> 00:02:59.320
But anyway,

00:02:59.800 --> 00:03:00.930
I'm quite satisfied

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:02.520
with my wife.

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:05.180
Now you're me, and I'm you.

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:06.280
She

00:03:06.920 --> 00:03:08.160
is my wife.

00:03:16.520 --> 00:03:17.560
I thought

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:19.420
she was pushed by circumstances,

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:20.980
and forced into marriage.

00:03:22.079 --> 00:03:24.140
But it turns out this was all her plan.

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:37.900
Stone King of Hell,

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:39.680
Yun Zhan,

00:03:43.880 --> 00:03:45.720
which one is your true identity?

00:03:47.160 --> 00:03:47.960
Both are.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:49.840
Yet not entirely.

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:54.720
I like them both.

00:03:57.880 --> 00:03:59.680
Why are you so determined to die?

00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:04.400
What do you mean?

00:04:08.240 --> 00:04:09.570
If you return to Mocheng

00:04:09.640 --> 00:04:11.570
and marry the Young Master of Xiqi,

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:12.810
at that time,

00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:14.680
the Phoenix Incense formula,

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.200
the Phoenix Seal,

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:16.260
and the black jade,

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.290
will all appear.

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:20.200
Meng Wu

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.880
will certainly try her best that day

00:04:21.880 --> 00:04:22.920
to kill you.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.460
You want to trade your life

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:27.000
for Xiqi's power.

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.260
Utilizing your marriage,

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:32.440
you want the Young Master of Xiqi

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:34.040
to eliminate Meng Wu for you.

00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:35.240
Am I right?

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:44.140
You've seen through everything.

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:47.440
You set up this trap yourself

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:48.970
and put yourself in danger.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:50.600
How am I supposed

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:51.520
to save you?

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:04.080
Mocheng

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.480
is the land

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:10.220
our Feng family has protected
for generations.

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:11.600
Protecting Mocheng

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:13.000
and its people

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:14.360
is my duty.

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:16.600
That's all

00:05:17.320 --> 00:05:18.360
I care about.

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:21.960
The Xin siblings are kind-hearted.

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.240
They won't make things difficult for
the new heir,

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:25.280
Feng Ling'er.

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.800
I will always be with you.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:46.600
We will get through this.

00:05:51.200 --> 00:05:52.280
So when do you plan

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.240
to tell me the truth,

00:05:56.320 --> 00:05:57.200
Little Stone？

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:10.720
You did recognize me.

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:16.920
You're the heir of Mocheng.

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:18.900
Why did you lie to me

00:06:19.280 --> 00:06:20.920
that you were a wandering beggar?

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:22.250
Your lie hurt me deeply.

00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:25.640
You betrayed me once,

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:27.450
and I deceived you once.

00:06:27.760 --> 00:06:29.120
Now we're even.

00:06:33.200 --> 00:06:34.840
The trip back to Mocheng is dangerous.

00:06:34.840 --> 00:06:37.159
This time, I must escort you back myself.

00:06:38.760 --> 00:06:40.420
Don't say such foolish words.

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:41.840
In Mocheng,

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:43.640
you're considered dead.

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:44.600
What identity will you use

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:46.330
to return to the palace with me?

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:48.690
The powerful Stone King of Hell

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:50.170
came back from the dead.

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.810
That's not impossible.

00:06:54.280 --> 00:06:55.440
Stone King of Hell

00:06:58.760 --> 00:07:00.600
failed in his assassination attempt

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:02.480
and would be escorted back to Mocheng

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:03.810
to await your judgment.

00:07:06.550 --> 00:07:08.820
[Fengling Hall]

00:07:09.350 --> 00:07:10.920
Ling'er, you looks pale.

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:12.400
How are you recently?

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:13.560
Aunt,

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.880
why did it take you so long to see me?

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.840
I've been confined for many days.

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:20.080
Nobody treats me as their master now.

00:07:20.640 --> 00:07:22.900
The Queen has married far away into Xiqi.

00:07:23.080 --> 00:07:25.360
I've been occupied with
matters to attend to.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:27.600
I meant to ask you to assist me,

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:29.680
but...

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:32.600
I planned to make a scene

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:33.800
on the departure day

00:07:33.880 --> 00:07:35.560
and refused to go to Xiqi
even if I killed myself

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:37.720
to make it difficult for Feng Li.

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:40.400
But she confined me.

00:07:40.640 --> 00:07:41.440
I'm not allowed to

00:07:41.440 --> 00:07:42.720
leave my palace.

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:46.000
She still has the nerve to
go for the political marriage herself.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:47.400
She is the dignified Queen of Mocheng.

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:49.000
But she brought such shame upon herself.

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:51.600
She is truly unworthy of
being a member of the Feng family.

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.460
Li has wandered since childhood.

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:55.520
Life has never been easy for her.

00:07:55.640 --> 00:07:57.000
When survival is at stake,

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:58.440
who will care about dignity?

00:07:58.440 --> 00:07:59.570
She may have no shame

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:00.920
but Mocheng does,

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:03.460
and so do we,
descendants of the Feng family!

00:08:03.760 --> 00:08:04.800
Aunt.

00:08:05.080 --> 00:08:06.160
Be good, Ling'er.

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:08.480
Now that Feng Li is gone,

00:08:08.760 --> 00:08:10.200
I will take care of you.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:12.600
We are members of the royal clan.

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.240
As long as she is the Queen,

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:15.680
I am inferior to her.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.440
Aunt.

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:22.680
If you don't want to be a bird in a cage,

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:24.920
you might as well take a chance.

00:08:25.440 --> 00:08:27.280
The half Tiger Tally your mother left you

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:28.480
before she died

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:30.210
can command the palace guards.

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.840
With the Tiger Tally,

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:34.280
you can break the deadlock.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:36.840
The Tiger Tally

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:40.960
was taken by Feng Li before she left.

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:48.200
What a pity.

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:50.560
I thought you were

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:52.560
a clever person.

00:08:53.640 --> 00:08:54.560
Aunt.

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:02.360
I came to see you before I leave.

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:04.280
This might be the last time

00:09:04.280 --> 00:09:05.740
we sisters see each other.

00:09:06.840 --> 00:09:08.960
Your Majesty, you are sending me away
for a political marriage.

00:09:08.960 --> 00:09:10.960
So, no one will be
in your way anymore, right?

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:12.720
I didn't come for small talk.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:15.170
I want you to give me something important,

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.240
your mother's Tiger Tally.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:18.320
I knew it.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:20.680
You didn't come with good intentions.

00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:22.540
So, you're after the Tiger Tally.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:25.440
My mother was the former Guardian General.

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.370
By tradition, both the Tiger Tally

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:29.130
and the general's position

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.680
should be passed to me.

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:33.000
You refused to grant me a title

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:35.050
and are sending me far away to Xiqi.

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:36.160
Isn't it just to

00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:37.560
eliminate me as a threat?

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.720
So, you know your mother was the

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:40.120
Guardian General, hugh?

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.480
You’re nothing but a spoiled fool!

00:09:44.520 --> 00:09:46.640
How can you be a daughter of our family?

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:48.640
How dare you have the nerve
to criticize me?

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:50.640
Do you think you’re any better?

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.440
Everyone in Mocheng

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:54.200
knows that you are indulging in
luxury and pleasure,

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.120
and living in complete debauchery.

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.920
Everyone calls you "Demon Lord"
behind your back.

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.320
If Aunt hadn't taken you in

00:10:01.560 --> 00:10:03.360
and managed everything for you,

00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:05.090
would you even be alive now?

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:09.520
How dare you hit me?

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:11.040
Yes.

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:12.000
Wake up!

00:10:12.880 --> 00:10:13.840
Use your brain

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.080
and think carefully.

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:17.930
I had been exiled for so many years.

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:19.080
I couldn't even pay respects to my mom

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.540
on her death anniversary.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.120
What real power do I have?

00:10:23.280 --> 00:10:24.840
Think about who it is

00:10:24.840 --> 00:10:26.480
that refuses to grant you a title.

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:28.880
Why does Xiqi want
a marriage alliance now?

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.040
The one who fears you

00:10:30.040 --> 00:10:31.200
and wants to send you away

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.480
is your dear Aunt.

00:10:32.680 --> 00:10:33.480
Impossible!

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:36.280
Aunt loves me the most.

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:37.880
It can't be.

00:10:46.040 --> 00:10:46.840
Ling'er.

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:50.120
You are kind-hearted and innocent.

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:54.210
After so many years by her side,

00:10:54.520 --> 00:10:55.440
of course you won't believe me

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:57.040
when I tell you these things.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.320
Let's make a bet.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.000
Do you dare?

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:04.120
What trick are you plotting now?

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:05.960
This bet concerns

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:08.240
Mocheng and its future.

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:10.600
You just want to take

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:11.640
my Tiger Tally

00:11:11.960 --> 00:11:14.200
and send me far away to Xiqi.

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:16.480
Why bother lying?

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:18.920
I know very well what's going on.

00:11:19.080 --> 00:11:20.810
The marriage alliance is real.

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:22.720
Someone will go to Xiqi.

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:26.500
But you're not the one.

00:11:26.840 --> 00:11:27.840
Then, who else?

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:30.720
Me.

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:39.600
Hide the Tiger Tally.

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:42.980
Meng Wu will come to ask you for it.

00:11:47.560 --> 00:11:48.800
You can tell her

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:50.440
that I took it.

00:11:51.400 --> 00:11:53.730
If she still treats you
the same as before,

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:55.360
then I lose.

00:12:00.040 --> 00:12:01.360
What if I win?

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:05.960
If you win,

00:12:08.080 --> 00:12:09.680
with the Tiger Tally in hand,

00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:11.640
you can overthrow me

00:12:12.760 --> 00:12:14.220
and take my place anytime.

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:32.960
She's mad.

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:37.100
She's asking me to rebel against her?

00:12:42.800 --> 00:12:44.400
Now that the Queen is absent,

00:12:44.600 --> 00:12:46.440
with the Phoenix Seal in my possession,

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:48.520
I am in charge of governing Mocheng.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:51.880
If you have the Tiger Tally
but refuse to hand it over,

00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:53.480
that would be defying orders.

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:54.280
I...

00:12:54.520 --> 00:12:55.980
Everything I said is true.

00:12:56.560 --> 00:12:58.080
Before Feng Li left,

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:00.080
she took the Tiger Tally.

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:01.520
Aunt, look,

00:13:01.520 --> 00:13:03.320
she left my palace in chaos.

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:05.160
Ling'er.

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:07.880
You're merely
an insignificant clan daughter.

00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:10.720
Even with the Tiger Tally,
what could you possibly do?

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:12.280
The Tiger Tally

00:13:12.360 --> 00:13:14.690
is nothing
but a pile of scrap metal to you.

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:16.640
It's not scrap.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:20.000
It's proof of
my mother's military achievements.

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:22.560
You are really like your mother,

00:13:22.760 --> 00:13:24.290
strong-willed and fierce.

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:25.840
However,

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:27.120
she's dead.

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:29.840
If you fail to choose wisely,

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:32.040
I'll kill you.

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:33.360
You...

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:35.240
Even if you kill me,

00:13:35.560 --> 00:13:36.800
I can't make it appear out of nowhere.

00:13:36.800 --> 00:13:37.680
Aunt.

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:45.680
Aunt.

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:48.760
You know I rely on you the most.

00:13:49.680 --> 00:13:51.800
How could you say such hurtful words?

00:13:53.480 --> 00:13:55.210
If I really had the Tiger Tally,

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:56.320
wouldn't I have used it

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:57.480
to deal with Feng Li?

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.160
In that case,

00:14:02.640 --> 00:14:04.160
your confinement

00:14:04.480 --> 00:14:05.840
will remain.

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:08.480
Stay in your mansion.

00:14:18.720 --> 00:14:20.360
Feng Li was right after all.

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:23.640
What should I do now?